      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six. This high-revving power unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS system for optimized valve timing across the rev range. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from documented rear subframe reinforcement\u2014a critical preventative measure for this platform. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivers precise engagement, while the variable M differential lock ensures linear power delivery through the rear wheels. Recent service includes rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment, ensuring internal tolerances remain within factory specification. This is a driver-focused example that balances raw performance with a diligent maintenance history.",
